\nGenerate search guidance specifically for Maps & Territory automation, including:\nplace categories to prioritize\nsearch queries to run\nradius strategy\nlocation targeting notes\nQuality Standard\nThe result must be:\nspecific\npractical\nbusiness-oriented\nuseful for lead discovery\nsuitable for AI scoring\nsuitable for sales/presales usage\nsafe to store in the product database\nFinal Instruction\nReturn only valid JSON. Do not include markdown. Do not include explanations outside the JSON.\n\nFeature input:\n{{input}}	f	t	1	1	2026-05-12 15:14:27	2026-05-12 15:14:23	2026-05-30 02:31:19
